{"id":614922,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ray_Thomas","text":"Raymond \"Ray\" Thomas (29 December 1941 \u2013 4 January 2018) was an English musician. He was best known as a flautist, singer and composer in the rock band, The Moody Blues.\nWorks.\nSome of his compositions are; \"Another Morning\" and \"Twilight Time\" (from \"Days of Future Passed\"), \"Dr. Livingstone, I Presume\" and \"Legend of a Mind\" (from \"In Search of the Lost Chord\"), \"Dear Diary\" and \"Lazy Day\" (from \"On the Threshold of a Dream\"), \"Eternity Road\", and \"Floating\" (from \"To Our Children's Children's Children\"), \"And the Tide Rushes In\" (from \"A Question of Balance\"), \"Our Guessing Game\" and \"Nice to Be Here\" (from \"Every Good Boy Deserves Favour\"), \"For My Lady\" (from \"Seventh Sojourn\"), and the medley \"Painted Smile/Reflective Smile/Veteran Cosmic Rocker\" (from \"Long Distance Voyager\").\nDeath.\nThomas died on 4 January 2018 of prostate cancer in Surrey at the age of 76.","categories":[],"infobox_types":[],"annotations":[{"uri":"English_people","surface_form":"English","offset":64},{"uri":"Musician","surface_form":"musician","offset":72},{"uri":"Flute","surface_form":"flautist","offset":105},{"uri":"Singing","surface_form":"singer","offset":115},{"uri":"Composer","surface_form":"composer","offset":126},{"uri":"Rock_music","surface_form":"rock","offset":142},{"uri":"Musical_ensemble","surface_form":"band","offset":147},{"uri":"The_Moody_Blues","surface_form":"The Moody Blues","offset":153},{"uri":"Another_Morning_(The_Moody_Blues_song)","surface_form":"Another Morning","offset":208},{"uri":"Twilight_Time_(The_Moody_Blues_song)","surface_form":"Twilight Time","offset":230},{"uri":"Days_of_Future_Passed","surface_form":"Days of Future Passed","offset":252},{"uri":"Dr._Livingstone%2C_I_Presume_(song)","surface_form":"Dr. Livingstone, I Presume","offset":278},{"uri":"Legend_of_a_Mind","surface_form":"Legend of a Mind","offset":311},{"uri":"In_Search_of_the